In this section, you can manage all aspects related to your health, for example, you can use the Therapies function to remind you of all the therapies and / or medicines that you have to take daily or on a definitive basis, or more simply you can mark all the pills that take. The health record can be your best ally to be able to quickly remember and display information about your general health, from details to measurements.
